_source.body:
Isabel Sanford was an American stage, film, and television actress and comedian best known for her role as Louise "Weezy" Mills Jefferson on the CBS sitcoms All in the Family and The Jeffersons. 

Born: August 29, 1917, Harlem, New York, United States
Died: July 9, 2004, Cedars-Sinai Medical Center, Los Angeles, California, United States 

Spouse: William Edward Richmond (m. 1945–1960)

Children: Sanford K. Sanford, Pamela Ruff, William Eric Richmond
